PRODUCT :
Create :    POST http://localhost:8090/api/v2/ecommerce/product/add-product
            {
                "productName": "mad angles",
                "price": "10.0",
                "description": "spicy, crispy"
            }

Retrieve -  all GET http://localhost:8090/api/v2/ecommerce/product/all
            by name GET http://localhost:8090/api/v2/ecommerce/product/get-product-name/mad%20angles
            by description GET http://localhost:8090/api/v2/ecommerce/product/get-product-description/microphone

Update -    by name PUT http://localhost:8090/api/v2/ecommerce/product/update-product-name/zudio%20tshirt
            {
                "price": 249
            }

            by description PUT http://localhost:8090/api/v2/ecommerce/product/update-product-description/ruled,%20spiral%20bound
            {
                "productName": "paperclip book"
            }

Delete :    DELETE http://localhost:8090/api/v2/ecommerce/product/delete-product/4

